Poland
December 2nd 2020
"Vaccine - who is it for first?

Coronavirus is a serious threat to our health and life. We want the most vulnerable people to benefit from vaccines in the first place, that is:

    health workers;
    residents of nursing homes and patients of health and care facilities;
    people over 60 years of age;
    services that support the fight against COVID-19 - incl. police and military."

